{"tid":2128210,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦 真係好辛苦","createTime":"2020-07-27T22:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T09:43:28.000Z","uid":201498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"14989de6302f125fdc51c156f4de5282b5f1a0c1","tid":2128210,"uid":201498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T22:30:42.000Z","msg":"鐘意一個人已經咁辛苦<br />\n點解你有辦法同時鐘意幾個人<br />\n我已經為你付出所有<br />\n點解你唔可以着緊我多D<br />\n有時想一死了之<br />\n但又怕你會內疚<br />\n不如你狠狠掉底我<br />\n咁我做乜嘢都唔會對你有影響<br />\n<br />\n識咗你咁耐<br />\n自從你踏入嚟我生活開始<br />\n我就成個人都改變咗<br />\n有好嘅都有壞嘅<br />\n我唔後悔<br />\n但我真係唔想冇咗你<br />\n<br />\n我已經唔再記得幾耐冇再喊過<br />\n我以為我呢世人已經唔會再喊<br />\n成晚個心已經好唔舒服<br />\n我咁講都係因為我太愛你<br />\n點解你唔可以安慰我少少<br />\n你次次都要喺我個心到用刀大大力咁割<br />\n次次割完就俾兩塊膠布我<br />\n即使係咁我都只係想講我好掛住你"},{"pid":"eeb1918fa28c08dfa1cff57fbf447cd3dce974fe","tid":2128210,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T22:32:21.000Z","msg":"付出不一定等同於收穫，要成長了樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79f6ed038155517027a1a7dab08a6b35efd9d2b","tid":2128210,"uid":19215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72b3b6821700c7fc6cf14c480ec93723700cd126","tid":2128210,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:39:11.000Z","msg":"早D訓啦，佢都唔care你"},{"pid":"5ecaceaf323d85a2a494a671063bbcb135435eed","tid":2128210,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T23:40:50.000Z","msg":"睇死你冇180cm"},{"pid":"602620e902188cf1d0b316aabe1b9427e62276be","tid":2128210,"uid":287099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:43:28.000Z","msg":"你試下主動搵番佢去講啦<br />\n可能人地仲等緊你去溝通"}]}